long_description: This second generation, environmentally friendly 12 oz. degreaser dissolves oil and grease gunk and frees sticky, gummed up parts without damaging seals. Less aggressive than citrus degreasers, easily cleans delicate components; will not attack elastomers, rubber seals, O-rings or plastic components. Approved for use on Grip Shift(R), including Polycarbonate X-Ray(TM) models; will not affect Shimano(R) seals even when soaked in a tank. Fully biodegradable; exceeds all V.O.C. and California CARB regulations; contains no citrus, glycol ether, alcohol distillates, phosphates or water. 12 oz. aerosol for maximum penetrations.
